{
  "texts": [
    "The graph of models that we study in Section 3.1 is the undirected \"model family tree\" of HuggingFace user mlabonne's model AlphaMonarch-7B foot_0.",
    "Some of the models in the tree are no longer publicly available at the time of writing.",
    "Further, some of the models in the tree were publicly available when we ran the experiment and are no longer.",
    "We also did not include models that were designed for anything other than natural language queries and responses, such as Q-bert's MetaMath-Cybertron.",
    "Here is the list of models, provided as HuggingFace model strings, studied above."
  ]
}